sec.p:
Picture labelling was carried out by three veterinarians (namely, observer A, B and C), who agreed to classify each porcine auricle as follows:
•Healthy auricles showing a normal silhouette (label 0);
•Deformed auricles displaying alterations in their contour, due to real lesions and regardless of their severity (label 1);
•Auricles showing postmortem artefacts, such as cuts or strains after brushing (label 2).
